# R Packages

[ggRandomForests: Visually Exploring randomForests](ggRandomForests) 

The ggRandomForests package extends the analytic plotting of [randomForestSRC](http://cran.r-project.org/web/packages/randomForestSRC/index.html) objects using [ggplot2](http://ggplot2.org/).
